sub_title: Electronics Lead at Avular | Organizer of Hardware Meetups | Product Developer
summary:
My passion is technology - understanding how things work, how they fit into our lives and mostly how to build them from the scratch is something that has always amazed and excited me.

I am very communicative, sociable, love team expert discussions and brainstorming. A part of my everyday life is learning new things and finding new ways to use them in my profession. 

I am currently located in Eindhoven (Netherlands).

EXPERTISE: 
• Product development (HW)
• Schematic design
• Multilayer PCB layout (high speed design)
• Defining custom stackups
• Designing PDN
• Prototyping, assembling and testning PCBs
• Documentation and instruction writing/drawing
• Enclosure design
